import React from 'react'
import {Nav} from 'react-bootstrap'
import {VscDashboard} from 'react-icons/vsc'

function ProductTable() {
    return (
        <Nav fill variant="tabs" defaultActiveKey="/home">
        <Nav.Item>
            <VscDashboard />
            <Nav.Link href="/home">Dashboard</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="link-1">Shop</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="link-2">Product Analysis</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="link-3">Sales Marketing</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="link-4">Financial Management</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="link-5">Reports</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="link-6">Configurations</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        </Nav>
    )
}

export default ProductTable
